      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-02032'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_105'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-conrad-russell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_105' title='Link to this speech by Mr Conrad Russell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-conrad-russell" title="Mr Conrad Russell">Earl Russell</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            It would be churlish of me not to add to the general unanimity and even more churlish of me to use more words in saying so.
          </p>
