          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-02148'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_221'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-emily-blatch' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_221' title='Link to this speech by Ms Emily Blatch' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-emily-blatch" title="Ms Emily Blatch">Baroness Blatch</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Minister is unusually touchy today.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-02149'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_222'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-bassam' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_222' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Bassam' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-bassam" title="Mr John Bassam">Lord Bassam of Brighton</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            No, I am not.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-02150'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_223'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-emily-blatch' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_223' title='Link to this speech by Ms Emily Blatch' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-emily-blatch" title="Ms Emily Blatch">Baroness Blatch</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Minister said that the amendment was flawed because it did not contain a definition. But the amendment is redefining lap dancing clubs. That is the point of the amendment. That is the point that he missed. The intention is to redefine lap dancing clubs and put them into the same
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_112gc' title='Col. 112GC &mdash; HL Deb 24 June 2003 vol 650 c112GC' name='column_112gc' href='#column_112gc' rel='bookmark'>112GC</a>
            category as sex shops. I think that it is a perfectly simple amendment and would be extremely responsive to those who are concerned in the community. I will leave it to my noble friend to make a judgment about the response that the Minister gave. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0650P0-02151'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030624_GCR_224' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
